</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="143" pageId="3" pageNumber="142" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="3.[775,1400,1590,1790]" lastBlockId="4.[189,813,1532,1791]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="143" pageId="3" pageNumber="142">
Diagnosis. Males of this species are very similar to those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1965" box="[801,930,1741,1760]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Helvetia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="142" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riojanensis">
<emphasis box="[801,817,1741,1759]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="142">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[830,930,1741,1759]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="142">riojanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the shape of the RTA (see 
<bibRefCitation author="GALIANO" box="[1223,1357,1740,1760]" firstAuthor="GALIANO" journalOrPublisher="Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina" pageId="3" pageNumber="142" pagination="47 - 50" part="27" refId="ref6489" refString="GALIANO, M. E. 1965. Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae). Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina 27: 47 - 50." title="Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae)" type="journal article" year="1965">GALIANO 1965</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 3), from which they can be distinguished by having a more slender cymbium seen in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[605,676,1532,1552]" captionStart="Figures 15-20" captionStartId="6.[189,256,1173,1193]" captionTargetBox="[352,1306,201,1167]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[344,1309,189,1172]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Figures 15-20. Left palp of (15-16) Helvetia galianoae: (15) ventral view̡ (16) retrolateral view; (17-18) Helvetia humillima: (17) ventral view̡ (18) retrolateral view; (19-20) Helvetia stridulans: (19) vental view̡ (20) retrolareal view. Bars = 0.25 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3678513" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3678513/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
) and shorter RTA branches (
<figureCitation box="[340,411,1562,1582]" captionStart="Figures 15-20" captionStartId="6.[189,256,1173,1193]" captionTargetBox="[352,1306,201,1167]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[344,1309,189,1172]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Figures 15-20. Left palp of (15-16) Helvetia galianoae: (15) ventral view̡ (16) retrolateral view; (17-18) Helvetia humillima: (17) ventral view̡ (18) retrolateral view; (19-20) Helvetia stridulans: (19) vental view̡ (20) retrolareal view. Bars = 0.25 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3678513" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3678513/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3678506" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3678506" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3678506/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" startId="4.[189,256,1381,1401]" targetBox="[201,1451,197,1372]" targetPageId="4">
<paragraph blockId="4.[189,1474,1298,1460]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">
Figures 4-10. Epigynum of (4-5) 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1976" box="[501,687,1381,1401]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Helvetia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cancrimana">
<emphasis box="[501,687,1381,1401]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Helvetia cancrimana</emphasis>
