<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="143" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[189,813,1532,1791]" lastBlockId="4.[850,1475,1532,1791]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">
Description. Male (
<typeStatus box="[434,526,1592,1612]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">holotype</typeStatus>
). Total length: 4.75. Carapace dark brown, 2.00 long, 1.25 wide, 0.90 high, with a narrow marginal stripe of white scales. Cephalic region black. Ocular quadrangle 0.90 long. Anterior eye row 0.95 wide and posterior 0.95 wide. Chelicera reddish brown. Endite, labium and sternum dark brown. Palp as in 
<figureCitation box="[485,639,1741,1761]" captionStart="Figures 15-20" captionStartId="6.[189,256,1173,1193]" captionTargetBox="[352,1306,201,1167]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[344,1309,189,1172]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Figures 15-20. Left palp of (15-16) Helvetia galianoae: (15) ventral view̡ (16) retrolateral view; (17-18) Helvetia humillima: (17) ventral view̡ (18) retrolateral view; (19-20) Helvetia stridulans: (19) vental view̡ (20) retrolareal view. Bars = 0.25 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3678513" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3678513/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Figs 15 and 16</figureCitation>
. Legs 1432, light brown, with longitudinal black stripes on the tibiae and metatarsi II-IV. Length of femur: I 1.05, II 0.75, III 0.80, IV 1.10; patella + tibia: I 1.70, II 0.95, III 0.95, IV 1.35; metatarsus + tarsus: I 0.90, II 0.60, III 0.90, IV 1.05. Spination. Femur I, II, III, IV d1- 1; tibia I 0, II 
<date box="[977,999,1622,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v1</date>
pr, III 
<date box="[1059,1082,1621,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v1</date>
di, IV 
<date box="[1141,1166,1621,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v2</date>
di; metatarsus I, II 
<date box="[1344,1389,1622,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v2-2</date>
, III 
<date box="[1425,1448,1621,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v1</date>
di, p1, r1, IV 
<date box="[955,979,1651,1671]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">v2</date>
di, p1, r1. Abdomen dark brown, with two transverse white marks. Anterior and posterior spinnerets brown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[850,1475,1532,1791]" box="[911,1103,1711,1731]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Female. Unknown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
